OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rising petrol prices have led to an    
OL,6, increase in fuel thefts from petrol    
OL,7, station forecourts, according to new   
OL,8, figures from industry experts.         
OL,10,FPetrol prices hit record highs last    
OL,11,Fweek, with the cost of filling a       
OL,12,Ftypical family car passing #100.       
OL,14,FForecourt Eye, which works with 1,000  
OL,15,Fgarages in the UK, said there was a 39%
OL,16,Fincrease in non-payments since January.
OL,18,FThese included motorists driving off   
OL,19,Fwithout paying or claiming to have     
OL,20,Fforgotten their wallet.                
